source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_SEQ_00<tab>789th Order Dustman Bo Zu's all-too-healthy appetite has gotten him into hot water.
target: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_SEQ_00<tab>第789洞穴団の採掘地のダストマン789 ボ・ズは、仲間を恐れているようだ。

source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_SEQ_01<tab>Bo Zu fears that he will incur the ire of the 789th's hot<var 1F /var>tempered acolyte, Ba Go, for munching on─of all things─the appendages of the latter's precious bombs. Travel to Iron Lake and pluck three digits from the hands of the grenades hovering about the area, that you might make amends for the gluttonous dustman's misdeeds.
target: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_SEQ_01<tab>ダストマン789 ボ・ズは、アコライト789 バ・ゴを怒らせてしまったそうだ。彼の機嫌を直すためには、ボムの材料を手に入れる必要があるらしい。アイアンレイクの「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2010E01 /var>」を討伐して「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E897201 /var>」を3個入手しよう。

source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_SEQ_02<tab>Three grenade digits are yours. Deliver them to Ba Go at the 789th Order Dig before he visits flaming destruction upon the rueful Bo Zu.
target: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_SEQ_02<tab><var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2010E01 /var>を倒して、<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E897201 /var>を入手した。第789洞穴団の採掘地の「アコライト789 バ・ゴ」に「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E897201 /var>」を渡そう。

source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_SEQ_03<tab>Ba Go was already wise to Bo Zu's misdeeds, having suffered similar antics before. He accepts the digits you have procured for him, but has little intention of forgiving his friend. Fortunately for Bo Zu, the acolyte is more concerned with mending his beauties than seeking revenge.
target: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_SEQ_03<tab>アコライト789 バ・ゴに<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E897201 /var>を渡した。しかし、彼はダストマン789 ボ・ズを許すつもりはないらしい。事の次第について、第789洞穴団の採掘地の「ダストマン789 ボ・ズ」に報告しよう。

source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_SEQ_04<tab>Sufficiently shaken by Ba Go's threats, Bo Zu will endeavor not to feast on the acolyte's beauties in the future. With the vain hope that the dustman's brain is stronger than his belly, you take your leave...
target: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_SEQ_04<tab>ダストマン789 ボ・ズに、アコライト789 バ・ゴの意向を伝えた。彼も、自分で謝りに行くべきだと理解しているようだが……。ダストマン789 ボ・ズが腹をくくれなかったときは、また背中を押してあげよう。

source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_TODO_00<tab>Defeat grenades to obtain grenade digits.
TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_TODO_01<tab>Deliver grenade digits to 789th Order Acolyte Ba Go.
target: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_TODO_01<tab>アコライト789 バ・ゴに<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E897201 /var>を渡す

source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_TODO_02<tab>Report to 789th Order Dustman Bo Zu.
target: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_TODO_02<tab>ダストマン789 ボ・ズと話す

source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BOZU_000_000<tab>Oh, I've done it this time! Yes, yes, I have. He will roast me─burn me, scorch me, roast me alive!
target:
TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BOZU_000_000<tab>マズーい　マズいんだーど……
アコライト789 バ・ゴを　怒らせちゃったんだーど。
バ・ゴの爆弾の材料　間違えて食べちゃったせいだーど……。

source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BOZU_000_001<tab>Who will? Ba Go will, with cackles, cackles and glee, for I snacked on the fingers of some of his beauties. Yes, yes, I did. But who can blame poor, hungry Bo Zu? Not you─no, no, not you.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BOZU_000_001<tab>このままーじゃ　爆弾で　ドッカンやられるーど。
オイーラ　痛いの　イヤなんだーど……
お願いだーど　なくなったボムの材料を　集めてほしいんだーど！

source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BOZU_000_002<tab>Please, adventurer! You must bring fiery fingers to Ba Go's workshop before he comes hunting for Bo Zu. You would not want to see poor Bo Zu burn, would you? No, no, you...probably shouldn't answer that.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BOZU_000_002<tab>「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2010E01 /var>」から「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E897201 /var>」を　手に入れーて！
それをバ・ゴに渡しーて　ご機嫌をとるんだーど！

source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BOZU_000_003<tab>Please, adventurer! You must bring fiery fingers to Ba Go's workshop before he comes hunting for Bo Zu. You would not want to see poor Bo Zu burn, would you? No, no, you...probably shouldn't answer that.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BOZU_000_003<tab>「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2010E01 /var>」から「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E897201 /var>」を　手に入れーて！
それをバ・ゴに渡しーて　ご機嫌をとるんだーど！

source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BAGO_000_020<tab>My beauties, dismembered again! I will burn every last hair from Bo Zu's body─yes, yes, Bo Zu will sear, sizzle, burn!
target:
TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BAGO_000_020<tab>ククク……ボクちゃんの爆弾作り……
邪魔しーた　ボ・ズを許さないーよ……
謝ったーって　ボムちゃんは　帰ってこないーよ……。

source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BAGO_000_021<tab>Fire fingers, you bring? To me, you say, from Bo Zu? Hah! That is a good laugh─cackle, chortle, laugh. In many, many years I have not seen Bo Zu lift a paw in the name of honest work. No, no, not a one.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BAGO_000_021<tab>ククク……これーは<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E897201 /var>……
これがあれーば　またボムちゃん作れーる……。
やるねチミ　見なおしたーよ　クーックク……。

source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BAGO_000_022<tab>I will not so easily forgive Bo Zu─no, no, never─but my poor, fingerless beauties demand my attention. Deliver to Bo Zu a warning─a caution, a threat, a warning. The next time he snacks in my workshop will be the last!
target:
TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BAGO_000_022<tab>でもボ・ズ　やっぱり　許せなーいよ……。
チミ　よこして　自分で謝らないのはダーメ……。
ボ・ズにも　そう伝えてーよ　ククク……！

source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BOZU_000_030<tab>Oh, thank you, adventurer! Ba Go said what!? <gulp> Tell me you jest─joke, tease, jest.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BOZU_000_030<tab>バ・ゴ　許してくれなかったーど？
しょうがないーど　悪いのは　オイーラだーど……。
行ってくれて　ありがとうだーと……。

source: TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BOZU_000_031<tab>But Bo Zu has learned his lesson. Besides, fire fingers are not easy on Bo Zu's belly─no, no, they make Bo Zu's belly burn. Yes, yes, Bo Zu's mind understands, but will his belly listen? This Bo Zu does not know...
target:
TEXT_BANKOB103_01327_BOZU_000_031<tab>トホホホ　これは　素直に怒られるしかないーど……。
アンータ　オイーラが　生きて帰れるよーに
せめて　祈ってほしいーど……。
